SWISS DAYBOOK: UBS Directors’ Meeting, Zuercher Kantonalbank

-- B y   L e i g h   B a l d w i n   a n d   K l a u s   W i l l e
-- 
2011-09-21T05:55:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/swiss-daybook-ubs-directors-meeting-zuercher-kantonalbank.html
UBS AG (UBSN) ’s directors will meet in
 Singapore , home to the Swiss bank’s biggest shareholder, today
to discuss the lender’s strategy and review the $2.3 billion
loss from unauthorized trading. The regular meeting was
scheduled before the loss emerged.  EQUITIES:
*Roche holds investor day in London
*Zuercher Kantonalbank said it may be the subject of an
investigation by U.S. authorities
* Basler Kantonalbank (BSKP)  names Dominik Galliker head of private
banking  ECONOMY/GOVERNMENT:
*Swiss parliament session in Bern
*Swiss and German governments to sign tax agreement at 4:30 p.m.
*SNB publishes monthly statistical bulletin at 9 a.m.  MARKETS:
*The SMI rose 2.1 percent to 5,471.40
*The SPI gained 1.9 percent to 4,987.21
*The Stoxx Europe 600 Index climbed 1.8 percent to 229.10
*The MSCI Asia-Pacific Index was up 0.4 percent at 7:53 a.m.
Zurich time
